latestPosts.caption:
#STYLEDBYSHIFAFIROZ #BRIDESBYSHIFAFIROZ 
Here’s one of our brides for this season! She has been styled in a sophisticated yet contemporary fashion, with her cherry red Manish Malhotra lehenga which serves as a refreshing break from the usual red shades. In addition to that, the lehenga has been styled with a mint green dupatta that adds a touch of radiance. Statement emerald pieces are used for jewellery to add the perfect contrast and finally, the hair and makeup pulls the whole look together.
